<plot>Runaway, the rock video is a stop motion animation music video shot featuring Luis Cardenas, the gregarious drummer from the rock bank Renegade in one of his solo album releases. The video starts with Cardenas answering a phone saying "So that's it? It's over?" signifying the end of a relationship. Cardenas then strolls down the street twirling drum sticks singing the intro to the Del Shannon song by the same name. Cardenas stumbles upon a junkyard with a massive drum set inside (which is Cardenas' record setting set). As Cardenas begins to play the drums, animated dinosaurs emerge as his co-stars.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?470583</url></doc>
